fm: bool searchMatrix(vector<vector<int>>& matrix, int target) {         if (matrix.empty() || matrix[0].empty()) return false;         int m = matrix.size();         int n = matrix[0].size();                  int i = 0, j = n - 1;         while (i < m && j >= 0) {             if (matrix[i][j] < target) {                 i++;             } else if (matrix[i][j] > target) {                 j--;             } else {                 return true;             }         }         return false;     }
